    <item>
      <title>【笔记】IDEA启动SpringBoot项目后Services窗口不显示端口号</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/27/IDEA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8SpringBoot%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8EServices%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%B7/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/27/IDEA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8SpringBoot%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8EServices%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%B7/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Apr 2021 07:14:57 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;IDEA启动SpringBoot项目后Services窗口不显示端口号&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>IDEA启动SpringBoot项目后Services窗口不显示端口号</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="解决问题"><a href="#解决问题" class="headerlink" title="解决问题"></a>解决问题</h2><ul><li>找到不显示端口号的运行中的Application-&gt;<code>Endpoints</code>-&gt;<code>Beans</code>-&gt;<code>application</code>-&gt;<code>刷新</code></li></ul><p><img src="/images/20210427151457/01.png" alt="01.png"></p><h2 id="强制刷新缓存（可选）"><a href="#强制刷新缓存（可选）" class="headerlink" title="强制刷新缓存（可选）"></a>强制刷新缓存（可选）</h2><ul><li><p>如果还是不显示，可以强制刷新IDEA缓存</p></li><li><p><code>File</code>-&gt;<code>Invalidate Caches</code></p></li></ul><p><img src="/images/20210427151457/02.png" alt="02.png"></p><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_41934688/article/details/112010282" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CSDN——我举个栗子吧</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      <comments>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/27/IDEA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8SpringBoot%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%8EServices%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%B7/#disqus_thread</comments>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>【踩坑】程序包org.springframework.boot不存在</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/27/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%8C%85org-springframework-boot%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/27/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%8C%85org-springframework-boot%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Apr 2021 06:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;IDEA运行SpringBoot项目报错：&lt;code&gt;程序包org.springframework.boot不存在&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>IDEA运行SpringBoot项目报错：<code>程序包org.springframework.boot不存在</code></p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="解决问题"><a href="#解决问题" class="headerlink" title="解决问题"></a>解决问题</h2><ul><li><p>将构建和运行交给Maven管理</p></li><li><p><code>IntelliJ IDEA</code>-&gt;<code>preference</code>-&gt;<code>Build, Execution, Deployment</code>-&gt;<code>Build Tools</code>-&gt;<code>Maven</code>-&gt;<code>Runner</code>-&gt;<code>Delegate IDE build/run actions to Maven</code></p></li></ul><p><img src="/images/20210427143918/01.png" alt="01.png"></p><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/chenghu/p/13912969.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">博客园——Mr. Li</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      <comments>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/27/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%8C%85org-springframework-boot%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8/#disqus_thread</comments>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>【笔记】关闭sitemap索引提示</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/23/%E5%85%B3%E9%97%ADsitemap%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/23/%E5%85%B3%E9%97%ADsitemap%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Apr 2021 12:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;微信小程序关闭sitemap索引提示&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>微信小程序关闭sitemap索引提示</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="关闭提示"><a href="#关闭提示" class="headerlink" title="关闭提示"></a>关闭提示</h2><p><em>project.config.json</em></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">"setting"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"checkSiteMap"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/framework/sitemap.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">微信小程序开发者文档</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
