    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>【笔记】发布npm包</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83npm%E5%8C%85/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83npm%E5%8C%85/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Apr 2021 06:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;发布npm包&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>发布npm包</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="创建账号"><a href="#创建账号" class="headerlink" title="创建账号"></a>创建账号</h2><ul><li>在<a href="https://www.npmjs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">npm官网</a>创建账号</li></ul><h2 id="在本地登陆"><a href="#在本地登陆" class="headerlink" title="在本地登陆"></a>在本地登陆</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm login</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Username: &#x2F;&#x2F; 输入用户名</span><br><span class="line">Password: &#x2F;&#x2F; 输入密码</span><br><span class="line">Email: &#x2F;&#x2F; 输入邮箱</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>登陆成功后，如果不是官方镜像源，可以修改镜像源</li></ul><p><a href="/2021/04/22/修改npm镜像/">传送门</a></p><h2 id="发布npm包"><a href="#发布npm包" class="headerlink" title="发布npm包"></a>发布npm包</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm publish</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1kv411W73u" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哔哩哔哩——Python小清风</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
